{"tid":280160,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【比特幣狂潮】Bitcoin升2.5%衝破3,000美元 黃金跌1%","createTime":"2017-06-12T01:19:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-12T01:19:38.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74ea9659d1beea266f901f7c819b06a679b8e95c","tid":280160,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-12T01:19:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170612/large/1497228790_cd1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170612%2Flarge%2F1497228790_cd1c.jpg&h=857173e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比特幣Bitcoin再創新高，Bitcoin一周前曾跌至2,600美元水平，價值亦坐過山車盤大上大落數次，到目前終於升穿3,000美元大關，最高曾見3,018美元，最新報3,012美元，升2.45%。<br />\n<br />\n另外，法國選情穩定，美股持續向好，避險情緒下降，金價一日內急跌14美元或1%，黃金每盎司報1,268美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56815814&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56815814%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170612&d=y2jl%2FZ68RTx3bFOKJOsQFL%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0f648c1b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56815814%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170612&h=75996f25\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56815814&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170612</a>"}]}